SANDBLAST
Evocation
Level: Druid 1
Components: V, S, DF
Casting Time: 1 standard action
Range: 10 ft.
Area: 10-ft.-radius burst centered
on you
Duration: Instantaneous
Saving Throw: Reflex half
Spell Resistance: Yes
Whipping your hand in a wide arc, you
spray sand from your fingers in a powerful
blast.
Creatures in the area take 1d6
points of nonlethal damage.
Any creature that fails its
Reflex save is also stunned for
1 round. You are not harmed
by the spell./